task.summary: Initial commit with partial package structure, required library and necessary gradle dependencies

Created a MessageOutputService that can be used by multiple message brokers. implemented 1 broker: RabbitMQ. Created formatting from Message object to xml string (classes are created but not filled). Created a test class with a basic setup for the message broker and a basic send method to test if data gets send to the message queue.

Working version of generating CreateOrderMessages. Sending to RabbitMQ works. Dto's are created but not implemented added logging output to console and file. Created test class with testing scenarios (no assertions tho)
Implemented the dto's and a basic CancelOrderMessage. Added functions to formatter and MessageOutputService for usage of those dto's
Fully working generator that sends create and cancel messages with all requirements from the pdf. Could still implement a Listener / MessageHandler
Recreated logfile with most recent run from complete test method
